{"tid":2213345,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"張達明：施覺民請辭三不尋常","createTime":"2020-09-22T12:38:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-22T13:25:49.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"efb5de7280db0c976f05ae78778fafae94ea2ed7","tid":2213345,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T12:38:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200922/4TGVYPNFRVD57AZUEKW3E3QZMY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200922%2F4TGVYPNFRVD57AZUEKW3E3QZMY%2F&d=o%2BIu8jl9TkUz6xxK8T5I2%2FCGrV5sAEOTHy2vWGvapoA%3D&h=464f51dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200922%2F4TGVYPNFRVD57AZUEKW3E3QZMY%2F&h=246453f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200922/4TGVYPNFRVD57AZUEKW3E3QZMY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n張達明：施覺民請辭三不尋常<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】終審法院非常任法官施覺民月初突然提出請辭，澳洲媒體引述消息指，施覺民辭任與港版國安法有關。港大法律學院首席講師張達明直言，今次事件令人非常憂慮，認為事件有三處「不尋常」地方，包括施覺民及政府未公開交代辭任原因，又認為事件無可避免影響國際社會對香港司法獨立信心。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/-BWItea2X3-I0s6ZeLNHoucfODw=/1277x851/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VS7IRWVWFFHPJKVTQGHIIJC7Y4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F-BWItea2X3-I0s6ZeLNHoucfODw%3D%2F1277x851%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVS7IRWVWFFHPJKVTQGHIIJC7Y4.gif&h=17ddde56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■施覺民突提請辭，張達明（圓圖）直言事件令人憂慮。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n影響國際對港司法信心<br />\n<br />\n張達明昨於港台節目中認為施覺民辭任令人非常憂慮，認為事件包含至少三處不尋常地方，包括健康未有問題的施覺民未有公開交代辭任原因、司法部門和特首未有交代施覺民辭職原因、特首亦未有按慣常做法表揚施覺民任內貢獻。<br />\n<br />\n對於有報道指施覺民辭任與港版國安法有關，有關說法十分合理，。。。。。。。。。，「今次係敲響咗一個好大嘅警鐘」，希望類似事件不會陸續有來。<br />\n<br />\n張達明又認為，。。。。。。。。。。，「佢哋（中央）話司法獨立係指有獨立審判權，內地嘅表述都話內地制度係有司法獨立」。<br />\n<br />\n對於近日有人建議終審法院可以考慮引入新加坡的法官出任非常任法官，張達明指《基本法》訂明聘用法官時，主要是考慮專業能力，香港回歸以來，委任的非常任法官都是國際認可傑出法官人才，「相對嚟講，新加坡（法官）係未及嗰個班數」，指在普通法體系下，澳洲、英國、加拿大的法官都獲國際認可。"},{"pid":"32819c9ef7e4cca6accb83111968542cc16a27ac","tid":2213345,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T12:41:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/stephendziedzic/status/1306835556601479168?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fstephendziedzic%2Fstatus%2F1306835556601479168%3Fs%3D21&d=o%2BIu8jl9TkUz6xxK8T5I2%2FCGrV5sAEOTHy2vWGvapoA%3D&h=35774874\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fstephendziedzic%2Fstatus%2F1306835556601479168%3Fs%3D21&h=87003577\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/stephendziedzic/status/1306835556601479168?s=21</a>"},{"pid":"2f9190e985ec7c1e3d3f30517e082facbd3b0e47","tid":2213345,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T12:44:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.abc.net.au/news/2020-09-18/judge-quits-over-hong-kong-national-security-law/12679318\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.abc.net.au%2Fnews%2F2020-09-18%2Fjudge-quits-over-hong-kong-national-security-law%2F12679318&d=o%2BIu8jl9TkUz6xxK8T5I2%2FCGrV5sAEOTHy2vWGvapoA%3D&h=052a4f14\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.abc.net.au/news/2020-09-18/judge-quits-over-hong-kong-national-security-law/12679318</a>"},{"pid":"1b0df04f4a89ed6add523f602ca54a8c92297b41","tid":2213345,"uid":85629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T13:04:19.000Z","msg":"仲敲響警鐘<br />\n喪鐘都敲到爛撚埋啦"},{"pid":"fd7db7712093341ec537ea8c2f8b1133f74905df","tid":2213345,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T13:05:08.000Z","msg":"仲敲響警鐘<br />\n個鐘係咪打仗既鐘"},{"pid":"1af47233ed6a455e09c1a3e37a027a59bba743ed","tid":2213345,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"efb5de7280db0c976f05ae78778fafae94ea2ed7","tid":2213345,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit