strong>"},{"pid":"10ed1d49c2f9235895ccf612b4575935ddd10c1e","tid":2213345,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T13:17:58.000Z","msg":"咩未有交代 咪講左同黨安法有關囉"},{"pid":"013594c0686392f597d20992c97931fd0eaeca68","tid":2213345,"uid":33522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T13:18:32.000Z","msg":"又認為事件無可避免影響國際社會對香港司法獨立信心。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好撚玩啦 <br />\n個特首同支聯辦都講撚到明香港係冇三權分立 即係根本冇司法獨立<br />\n<br />\n冇既野點樣失去信心"},{"pid":"2b3ca50a78e3bb8e5b4ba2fafeef2aa4d7d2af13","tid":2213345,"uid":119232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T13:25:49.000Z","msg":"有咩休慮姐<br />\n傻既都知la"}]}